<reference id="copyright" xml:lang="en-us">
   <title>
      <keyword>copyright</keyword>
   </title>
   <shortdesc>The &lt;<keyword>copyright</keyword>&gt; element is used for a single
copyright entry. It includes the copyright years and the copyright holder.
 Multiple &lt;<keyword>copyright</keyword>&gt; statements are allowed.</shortdesc>
